text: "It's All Over Now" is a song written by Bobby Womack and was first released in 1964 by The Valentinos. It was covered by The Rolling Stones and went to number 1 in the United Kingdom and the Netherlands, number 2 in New Zealand, Sweden and Ireland and number 9 in Australia. It has covered by numerous artists since its release.
